Package pokemonhotel

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    HotelAssistant
    An object of class HotelAssistant holds information on assistants that will be potentially taking care of pokemons
    HotelRoom
    An object of the class HotelRoom holds its room number, its resistance rating and its assigned Pokemon in case there is one
    Menu
    This class contains a method that keeps displaying a menu to the user until they decide to exit the program
    Pokemon
    An object of the class Pokemon holds the pokemon's name, its type, its unique stamp number, its Special Attack Rating, its Speed Rating and its Expert Level
    PokemonAccommodator
    This class contains a static method that uses data coming from the Setup object to assign pokemons to rooms and assistants
    PokemonHotel
    Driver class for the Pokemon Hotel program
    Setup
    An object of the class Setup holds all the information on the pokemons, assistants and hotel rooms it creates.
    Utilities
    This class contains useful methods that are used throughout the program for optimisation of the code
